{"tw": {"3668560": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "幸福島幻想", "steam_appid": 3668560, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [4306470], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲劇情</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒險家「謝冠宇」帶領一支探險小隊，調查常年風暴肆虐的漩渦中心，結果探險船在風暴中解體。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >昏迷中被海水沖刷到了一個幾乎與世隔絕的小島。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >醒來後，村長告訴他這裡是「幸福島」，想要離開就要等待下一次「祭祀日」，於是「謝冠宇」就暫住了下來。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在這裡他結識了幾位美麗的女孩，村長的女兒、嫵媚的未亡人、神秘的女神、新婚的少婦等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在這些紅顏知己的幫助下，成功解開了島上風暴的秘密，並發現了遠古的寶藏，然而這背後卻蘊藏著一個陰謀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幸福島的故事由此開始......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲元素</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【1】全島自由移動，跟隨玩家的操作肆意閒逛互動；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【2】釣魚、拾荒、種植、烹飪、挖掘作物等日常玩法；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【3】每個故事流程中都穿插小遊戲，互動感十足；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【4】豐富的動態CG動畫，每個細節動感十足；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【5】持續更新的遊戲內容，讓遊戲豐富度滿點；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668560/extras/66562da161bccecf56cddfda0ac48b94.avif?t=1770950445\" width=600 height=338 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668560/extras/91589118043d9f0f7beb444d068d7c93.avif?t=1770950445\" width=600 height=344 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瑪格麗特：村長的女兒，對外面的世界充滿嚮往，紫色的長髮，身材凹凸有致。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668560/extras/1df8237408a757b296ffdc3c03926ef9.webp?t=1770950445\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668560/extras/1df8237408a757b296ffdc3c03926ef9.poster.avif?t=1770950445