0": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Happy Island Fantasy", "steam_appid": 3668560, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [4306470], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Storyline</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adventurer “Ron” leads an expedition team to investigate the storm-ravaged vortex center, but their ship is torn apart in the storm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Washed ashore unconscious on a nearly isolated island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upon waking, the village head informs him that this is “Happy Island,” and to leave, he must wait for the next “Sacrifice Day,” so “Ron” temporarily stays.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here, he meets several beautiful girls: the village head’s daughter, a charming widow, a mysterious goddess, a newlywed young woman, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the help of these confidantes, he successfully unravels the secret of the island’s storms and discovers ancient treasures, but a conspiracy lurks behind it all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story of Happy Island begins here...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Elements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[1] Free movement across the island, interacting freely based on player actions;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[2] Daily activities like fishing, scavenging, planting, cooking, and harvesting crops;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[3] Mini-games woven into each storyline for immersive interaction;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[4] Rich dynamic CG animations, with every detail full of vitality;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[5] Continuously updated game content for maximum richness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/a