conscious on a nearly isolated island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upon waking, the village head informs him that this is “Happy Island,” and to leave, he must wait for the next “Sacrifice Day,” so “Ron” temporarily stays.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here, he meets several beautiful girls: the village head’s daughter, a charming widow, a mysterious goddess, a newlywed young woman, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the help of these confidantes, he successfully unravels the secret of the island’s storms and discovers ancient treasures, but a conspiracy lurks behind it all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story of Happy Island begins here...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Elements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[1] Free movement across the island, interacting freely based on player actions;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[2] Daily activities like fishing, scavenging, planting, cooking, and harvesting crops;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[3] Mini-games woven into each storyline for immersive interaction;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[4] Rich dynamic CG animations, with every detail full of vitality;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[5] Continuously updated game content for maximum richness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668560/extras/66562da161bccecf56cddfda0ac48b94.avif?t=1770950445\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668560/extras/91589118043d9f0f7beb444d068d7c93.avif?t=1770950445\" width=600 height=344 /></span>Margaret: The daughter of the village chief, full of yearning for the outside world, with long purple hair and a curvy figure.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668560/extras/1df8237408a757b296ffdc3c03926ef9.webp?t=1770950445\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668560/extras/1df8237408a757b296ffdc3c03926ef9.poster.avif?t=1770950445\" class=\"bb_img\" width=432 height=436 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sophia: A native girl of Xingfu Village, with yellow hair, gentle personality and thin figure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668560/extras/4697547d6bd6a1726ecbd02cb0cd2cf1.webp?t=1770950445\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668560/extras/4697547d6bd6a1726ecbd02cb0cd2cf1.poster.avif?t=1770950445\" class=\"bb_img\" width=432 height=436 /></picture></span>                        </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Olivia: A widow whose husband died early, a convenience store owner, with big and sexy breasts, a beauty in the hearts of the men in the village.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668560/extras/aab8364384880770dda94166dfb8165a.webp?t=1770950445\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668560/extras/aab8364384880770dda94166dfb8165a.poster.avif?t=1770950445\" class=\"bb_img\" width=432 height=436 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ilia: A mysterious goddess, seemingly here to fulfill a divine mission, dressed in light blue, exuding a sacred aura.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668560/extras/6b3b3d26692186e804f88a3053bf6786.webp?t=1770950445\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_it